@mAKEkr Blocking the domains does not help to block adverts protected by Ad-Shield.
To block Ad-Shield adverts and analytics, please install [microShield userscript](https://github.com/List-KR/microShield).
Its installation instruction written in Korean language is available at https://community.list-kr.com/docs/AdGuard/Userscripts/microShield.
